{
  "text": "SwIAVs isolated after two serial passages in MDCK or CACO-2 cell culture [CITATION_1] and preliminarily subtyped at the time of collection (Chiapponi, Moreno, Barbieri, Merenda, & Foni, 2012; [CITATION_2] ",
